PrecisEnactment of the RANKIN INLET AIRPORT ZONING REGULATIONS - which, for the purposes of aeronautical safety, impose the usual limits on the height of new or existing structures erected within a four-kilometre radius of the airport situated near Rankin Inlet, in the Northwest Territories.
